title.Name: title
title.Value: Snorkelling with my GoPro Hero 3 Silver and a Hawaiian Sling

description.Name: description
description.Value:
Just went for a swim with my mate to have a go at spearing a few fish with the hawaiian sling, just for some bait to take fishing and a bit of fun and target practice. I had a burst ear drum at the time so I couldn't dive under the water.. I was just spearing them from the surface... I hope you like the video.. its the first time i took my gopro diving so let me know what you think... I did see a few butterfish that day so I will be having a go at them when my ear has healed and I might try and put up a video of that :)

Cheers for watching :)
